import React from 'react'
import { InputContainer, InputWrapper, Form, Input, TextField } from './InputElements';

function InputForm() {
    return (
        <>
            <InputContainer>
                <InputWrapper>
                    <Form>
                        <Input>
                        </Input>
                    </Form>
                </InputWrapper>
            </InputContainer>
        </>
    )
}

export default InputForm
